{"tid":1310121,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【反修例】涂謹申：林鄭應命令警務處長撤回暴動定性","createTime":"2019-07-12T13:51:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-12T15:17:33.000Z","uid":212626,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"5338633c4e43980d322c87eed815453bcaa2ea87","tid":1310121,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T13:51:46.000Z","msg":"《逃犯條例》修訂爭議未息，雖然特首林鄭月娥及警務處處長盧偉聰曾以「暴動」來形容6月12日的金鐘警民衝突，但其後盧偉聰先改口稱從未將當日集會定性為「暴動」，只是個別人士使用暴力是「暴動」，林鄭月娥之後亦跟隨警方講法。不過，民陣今日(12日)展示6月12日晚上警方去信反對民陣於6月13日及14日繼續舉行集會，原因是已將當日集會定性為暴動，斥林鄭及「一哥」講大話。立法會議員涂謹申促林鄭月娥應明確指示盧偉聰撤回612暴動定性。<br />\n<br />\n民陣今日(7月12日)公開警方6月12日的發信，表明警方已當日集會定性為「暴動」，因而反對民陣之後2日舉辦的公眾活動。涂謹申認為，<span style=\"color: red;\">如林鄭月娥真的不同意6月12日的集會暴動，應根據《警隊條例》第4條，命令警務處長撤回警方6月12日給民陣的信函，以顯示特首並不同意信函中對6月12日當天的活動定性為暴動。</span><br />\n<br />\n涂謹申認為，只有這樣，民陣日後再申請遊行集會活動時，就不會給警方或有關的上訴委員會有藉口或誤解，<span style=\"color: red;\">以為民陣曾舉辦過暴動性質的活動，而認為民陣或無能力舉行和平的遊行集會，不會妨礙民陣往後申請遊行集會「不反對通知書」。</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2399112/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2399112%2F&d=f11PFKDsvG%2B7MRfNo%2B80BQjMvzJQG4GdM8cyRMJzdLg%3D&h=7fa2942f\" target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2399112/</a>"},{"pid":"d5b7d28198da3f864efc1ab4f8d43cd97e0e3d05","tid":1310121,"uid":212626,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T13:52:34.000Z","msg":"《警隊條例》第4條<br />\n處長管理警隊<br />\n在符合行政長官的命令及管制下，處長對警隊負有最高指示及管理責任。"},{"pid":"31f8c6f0bb642bf16ff2f0b664dd08e211fb4139","tid":1310121,"uid":55010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T13:53:28.000Z","msg":"屌你 又縮林鄭"},{"pid":"4c6bfdfd0acb9b96997424b1edf114e17d680175","tid":1310121,"uid":65790,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T13:58:33.000Z","msg":"暴動定性未收回影響左極多義士<br />\n第一會隨時俾人告暴動<br />\n第二義士傷左保險唔賠<br />\n<br />\n一定要撤回暴動定性，撤回暴動定性係有極大實質作用"},{"pid":"bbf08dec36ae4e07bd085ec5737c00880e9d3b5a","tid":1310121,"uid":259329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T13:59:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d3098dd6d76326d4de162e701501f4b16336bb6b","tid":1310121,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T14:04:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3020f56ab15d757871e50968c691e7b48f3affd7","tid":1310121,"uid":69013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T14:07:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ee4bef17cb47382370f0e805b4d3d4b4ff10de1","tid":1310121,"uid":160605,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T14:07:48.000Z","msg":"盧偉聰：警方決定『<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">暫緩</span></span>』暴動定性，並指該信函已『<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">壽終正寢</span></span>』。the mail is <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">dead</span></span>"},{"pid":"5a134f9780290cf595b6fa9cdd18c34e590d5c6e","tid":1310121,"uid":278893,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T14:22:33.000Z","msg":"仆街林鄭真係毫無誠信可言<br />\n所以咩壽終正寢真係唔撚洗信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99e8d62ff10015668e483831fa6f35fa5fd93d5d","tid":1310121,"uid":213379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T14:24:18.000Z","msg":"七 月 十 三 ！光 復 上 水 ！踢 走 水 貨 客！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1310098\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1310098</a><br />\n<br />\n【推上熱門】713光復上水資料<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1309441\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1309441</a><br />\n<br />\n[714/721] 野餐及夢遊服飾<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1309156\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1309156</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">集中火力推Post</span></span>"},{"pid":"4ded85da79b6ad67a4320066081a39ebe8af38ee","tid":1310121,"uid":52090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cite